Class PPodVersionInfo

java.lang.Object

      edu.upenn.cis.ppod.model.PPodVersionInfo
All Implemented Interfaces:
IPersistentObject
public final class PPodVersionInfo
extends PersistentObject

Stores data about a particular version of the whole pPOD instance - for example the pPOD version number.

The constructors and mutators of this class are intentionally package-private because we don't want for these to be manipulated outside of this package due to their trickiness.

Author:
Sam Donnelly
